    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative engineering: the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to address chassis fatigue common in this platform. Performance is enhanced by a Bilstein PSS10 coilover kit, providing adjustable damping and improved roll stiffness without sacrificing street compliance. The limited-slip differential remains tight, and the individual throttle bodies offer instantaneous throttle response. While the exterior shows minor road patina, the drivetrain and suspension geometry are dialed in for the serious driver.",
