    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Luxury AWD SUV in Midnight Sapphire Metallic. This vehicle has served our family well and remains in reliable, impressive condition. The exterior paint retains a deep luster, though upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. The interior features premium parchment leather; the seats are free of rips or stains, though there is natural softening and light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster from regular use. All electronics, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection performed last month. The tires are matching Continentals with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that offers a quiet, comfortable ride. It isn't a showroom trailer queen, but it is a high-quality, dependable driver that looks sharp in any driveway.",
